pothan &lt;unk&gt; ( malayalam : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; ) is a 2006 malayalam film directed by shaji kailas and written by renji panicker . the film stars mammootty , kausalya , jagathy sreekumar , kpac lalitha , aranmula ponnamma and kottayam santha in lead roles . the film had musical score by mb sreenivasan .